# Dynamic Tensor Rematerialization

This file is a transition-time build anchor for the public page.
The canonical publication record and assets live in `pubs/2021-iclr-dtr/`.

Edit `pubs/2021-iclr-dtr/publication.json` for structured publication data,
keep the abstract/BibTeX/assets in the same directory, and use
`pubs/2021-iclr-dtr/extra.dj` for any rare page-specific extra content.
